1 Be it enacted by the People of the State of Maine as follows:
2 Sec. 1. 29-A MRSA §1605, sub-§1, ¶C, as amended by PL 2023, c. 395, Pt. A,
3 §1, is further amended to read:
4 C. Be in the amount or limit of at least:
