3311 This bill repeals the laws requiring motor vehicle liability coverage in an amount up to
3322 $500 per accident for the towing and storage charges incurred as a result of an accident
3333 involving the insured vehicle if the vehicle is towed at the request of a law enforcement
3344 officer.
